        </h2>\r\n          \r\n          <div class=\"space-y-4\">\r\n            \r\n            \r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/chloe-kim-historic-three-peat-bid\" class=\"block p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600/30 to-rose-600/30 rounded-lg hover:from-red-600/40 hover:to-rose-600/40 transition-colors border-2 border-red-500 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🏂</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\r\n                    <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider bg-gradient-to-r from-red-600 to-red-700 text-white animate-pulse\">\r\n                      🔴 Breaking\r\n                    </span>\r\n                    <span class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">Just now • Snowboarding</span>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-red-200\">\r\n                    Chloe Kim Faces Unfamiliar Hurdles in Historic Three-Peat Bid\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-200 text-lg\">\r\n                    American snowboarding icon confronts wrist injury, fierce competition, and immense expectations as she pursues unprecedented third consecutive Olympic halfpipe gold medal.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            \r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/usa/malinin-surges-into-lead-olympic-figure-skating\" class=\"block p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600/20 to-cyan-600/20 rounded-lg hover:from-blue-600/30 hover:to-cyan-600/30 transition-colors border-2 border-blue-500/50 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">⛸️</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\r\n                    <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider bg-blue-600 text-white\">\r\n                      🔴 Breaking\r\n                    </span>\r\n                    <span class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">1 hour ago • Figure Skating</span>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-300\">\r\n                    Malinin Surges Into Lead in Olympic Men's Figure Skating\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    Ilia Malinin scores 108.16 points with two quad jumps and signature backflip, leading by five points over Japan's Yuma Kagiyama.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/usa/team-usa-wins-two-skiing-silvers\" class=\"block p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600/20 to-cyan-600/20 rounded-lg hover:from-blue-600/30 hover:to-cyan-600/30 transition-colors border-2 border-blue-500/50 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🎿</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\r\n                    <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider bg-blue-600/80 text-white\">\r\n                      Breaking\r\n                    </span>\r\n                    <span class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">2 hours ago • Skiing</span>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-300\">\r\n                    Team USA Wins Two Skiing Silvers at Milano Cortina\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    Alex Hall earns silver in freestyle slopestyle while Ben Ogden captures silver in cross-country sprint classic, ending a 50-year medal drought.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            \r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/swiss-skier-von-allmen-wins-third-gold\" class=\"block p-6 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-600/20 to-pink-600/20 rounded-lg hover:from-purple-600/30 hover:to-pink-600/30 transition-colors border-2 border-purple-500/50 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🥇</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mb-2\">\r\n                    <span class=\"inline-flex items-center px-2 py-1 rounded text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wider bg-gradient-to-r from-pink-500 to-purple-500 text-white\">\r\n                      � Historic\r\n                    </span>\r\n                    <span class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">3 hours ago • Alpine Skiing</span>\r\n                  </div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-purple-300\">\r\n                    Swiss Skier von Allmen Wins Third Gold, Joins All-Time Greats\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    Franjo von Allmen secured his place among Alpine skiing's legends, winning men's super-G to claim his third gold medal in five days. Only the third male skier to win three events at a single Winter Olympics, joining Killy and Sailer.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/usa-sweeps-gold-silver-in-womens-moguls\" class=\"block p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🥇</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2\">4 hours ago • Freestyle Skiing</div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">\r\n                    USA Sweeps Gold, Silver in Women's Moguls at Winter Olympics\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    Team USA dominated the women's moguls competition at Milano Cortina, sweeping the gold and silver medals in a spectacular display of freestyle skiing excellence on the Italian slopes.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/usa/team-usa-wins-five-medals-across-five-sports\" class=\"block p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🏅</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2\">Earlier Today • Multiple Sports</div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">\r\n                    Team USA Wins Five Medals Across Five Sports in Single Day\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    Historic achievement includes Team USA's first-ever mixed doubles curling medal. Cory Thiesse and Korey Dropkin earn silver, plus breakthroughs in cross-country skiing and three additional medals.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            \r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/lindsey-vonn/emergency-surgery-after-crash\" class=\"block p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🚨</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2\">Earlier Today • Alpine Skiing</div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">\r\n                    Lindsey Vonn Undergoes Emergency Surgery After Crash at Olympics\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    American ski legend airlifted to Milan hospital after devastating crash during Olympic downhill event. \r\n                    Emergency ACL reconstruction performed. Stable condition following three-hour surgery.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/italy-first-gold-lollobrigida\" class=\"block p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🥇</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2\">February 7, 2026 • Speed Skating</div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">\r\n                    Italy Wins First Gold as Milano Cortina Olympics Open\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    Francesca Lollobrigida set an Olympic record in women's 3,000-meter speed skating on her 35th birthday, \r\n                    thrilling the home crowd and securing Italy's first gold medal of the Games.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/lindsey-vonn-training-downhill\" class=\"block p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">⛷️</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2\">February 7, 2026 • Alpine Skiing</div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">\r\n                    Lindsey Vonn Posts Third-Fastest Training Time Before Olympic Downhill\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    The 41-year-old American skied on a torn ACL nine days after her crash, finishing 0.37 seconds \r\n                    behind teammate Breezy Johnson. Legendary performance ahead of Saturday's race.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/news/opening-ceremony-recap\" class=\"block p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🎭</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2\">February 7, 2026 • Opening Ceremony</div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">\r\n                    Milano Cortina Opens with Spectacular Ceremony Celebrating Italian Heritage\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    The 2026 Winter Olympics officially began with a stunning opening ceremony in Milano, \r\n                    featuring performances celebrating Italy's art, culture, and Olympic history.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/news/team-usa-roster\" class=\"block p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🇺🇸</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2\">February 6, 2026 • Team USA</div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">\r\n                    Team USA Announces Final Roster: 230 Athletes Across All Winter Sports\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    The United States Olympic Committee unveiled its complete roster for Milano Cortina 2026, \r\n                    featuring returning champions and exciting newcomers.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/news/climate-concerns\" class=\"block p-6 bg-white/5 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"flex items-start gap-4\">\r\n                <div class=\"text-3xl\">🌡️</div>\r\n                <div class=\"flex-1\">\r\n                  <div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 mb-2\">February 5, 2026 • Climate</div>\r\n                  <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">\r\n                    Warm Temperatures Raise Concerns for Outdoor Events\r\n                  </h3>\r\n                  <p class=\"text-gray-300\">\r\n                    Unusually warm weather in the Italian Alps has organizers monitoring conditions closely \r\n                    and preparing backup plans for snow-dependent events.\r\n                  </p>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n            </a>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"mt-6 text-center\">\r\n            <a \r\n              href=\"/winter-olympics/news\" \r\n              class=\"inline-block bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold transition-colors\"\r\n            >\r\n              View All Olympic News →\r\n            </a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <section class=\"bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 mb-8 border border-white/10\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3\">\r\n            <span class=\"text-3xl\">⭐</span>\r\n            Athletes to Watch\r\n          </h2>\r\n          \r\n          <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/athletes/mikaela-shiffrin\" class=\"bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">⛷️</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">Mikaela Shiffrin</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-2\">Alpine Skiing (USA)</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">\r\n                Most decorated alpine skier in World Cup history, aiming for multiple medals in her fourth Olympics.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/athletes/nathan-chen\" class=\"bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">⛸️</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">Nathan Chen</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-2\">Figure Skating (USA)</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">\r\n                Defending Olympic champion and six-time U.S. champion returns to defend his gold medal.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/athletes/johannes-boe\" class=\"bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">🎯</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">Johannes Thingnes Bø</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-2\">Biathlon (Norway)</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">\r\n                Dominant biathlete with 5 Olympic golds, seeking to cement legacy as greatest of all time.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/athletes/chloe-kim\" class=\"bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">🏂</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">Chloe Kim</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-2\">Snowboarding (USA)</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">\r\n                Two-time Olympic halfpipe champion looking to make history with third consecutive gold.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/athletes/eileen-gu\" class=\"bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">🎿</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">Eileen Gu</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-2\">Freestyle Skiing (China)</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">\r\n                Three-time Beijing 2022 medalist returns as one of winter sports' biggest stars.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </a>\r\n\r\n            <a href=\"/winter-olympics/athletes/shoma-uno\" class=\"bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors border border-white/10 group\">\r\n              <div class=\"text-4xl mb-3\">⛸️</div>\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-blue-400\">Shoma Uno</h3>\r\n              <p class=\"text-gray-400 mb-2\">Figure Skating (Japan)</p>\r\n              <p class=\"text-sm text-gray-300\">\r\n                World champion and Olympic bronze medalist aiming for gold on Italian ice.\r\n              </p>\r\n            </a>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n          <div class=\"mt-6 text-center\">\r\n            <a \r\n              href=\"/winter-olympics/athletes\" \r\n              class=\"inline-block text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 font-semibold\"\r\n            >\r\n              View All Athletes →\r\n            </a>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </section>\r\n\r\n        \r\n        <section class=\"bg-white/5 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-xl p-8 mb-8 border border-white/10\">\r\n          <h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6 flex items-center gap-3\">\r\n            <span class=\"text-3xl\">🏟️</span>\r\n            Competition Venues\r\n          </h2>\r\n          \r\n          <div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6\">\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/10\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Milano Cluster</h3>\r\n              <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-300\">\r\n                <li>• <strong>Ice Arena</strong> - Ice hockey</li>\r\n                <li>• <strong>Mediolanum Forum</strong> - Figure skating, short track</li>\r\n                <li>• <strong>PalaItalia</strong> - Curling</li>\r\n                <li>• <strong>Speed Skating Oval</strong> - Speed skating</li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n\r\n            <div class=\"bg-white/5 rounded-lg p-6 border border-white/10\">\r\n              <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-3\">Cortina d'Ampezzo Cluster</h3>\r\n              <ul class=\"space-y-2 text-gray-300\">\r\n                <li>• <strong>Cortina Olympic Stadium</strong> - Opening/closing ceremonies</li>\r\n                <li>• <strong>Tofana</strong> - Alpine skiing (downhill, super-G)</li>\r\n  